}}</ref>。

促成罢工结束的事件包括11月在[[卡斯尔福德矿区|卡斯尔福德矿区]]工作的一个矿工受到攻击<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.pontefractandcastlefordexpress.co.uk/news/We-want-your-striking-memories.4922977.jp|title=We want your striking memories|last=Wardill|first=Joanna|date=2009-01-29|accessdate=2009-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090202165234/http://www.pontefractandcastlefordexpress.co.uk/news/We-want-your-striking-memories.4922977.jp|archive-date=2009-02-02|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，12月在南威尔士州一名送一个矿工出工的出租车司机被误杀<ref name="Times">Tim Jones, "Two miners charged with murder of taxi driver", ''The Times'', 1 December 1984.</ref>。这场罢工没有达到1970年代那场先前罢工导致的停电和能源管制的广泛影响，电力公司在冬天的用电高峰期仍能保障电力供应<ref>{{cite news
|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/onthisday/hi/dates/stories/march/3/newsid_2515000/2515019.stm
